8) The mode string in the RRQ and WRQ is there
to signify whether to send the data in 16 bit
Ascii or in the 8 bit ascii. I chose to always
send in the 8 byte ascii code because the
the rfc specifies that the 16 byte Ascii exposes
a vulnerability.

9)when a POST request is made to the server, it replies
with the statuscode 501 not implemented. This is specified
in RFC 2616
